<br>
<br>
For those who have not been there in a while the sirens seem to be dispelling alot more than before, their slows land about 75% of the time even though my MR was 175+ and they have added a fear2 type spell that stuns/mezzes you for about 20 seconds, but has no icon on your screen and is not broken by you taking damage. I suggest pulling without symbol or you will bankrupt your cleric.<br>
